    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't want a \"quiet place\" to exist in. i just feel like everyone would be fine without me. like, there would just be one less person consuming resources and taking up space. doesn't it feel more logical that if someone is just a net negative or a void, then just... fading away is more peaceful for everyone involved? including me?",
